[normal]Between
[normal] Newton Abbot 
[normal]and
[normal] Paignton, the train takes 15 minutes, the bus 40 to 50 minutes.
[normal]   
[normal]Four
[normal] 
[normal]service
[normal]s 
[normal] run every 15 
[normal] or 20 
[normal]minutes during the day Mondays to Saturdays and half-hourly in the evenings and on Sundays. 
[normal]27.  
[normal]O
[normal]ther services
[normal] run 
[normal]less frequently
[normal] and
[normal] rarely or  
[normal]not at all in the evenings or on Sundays.  This means that for those living in 
[normal]most of Torbay
[normal],  no public tr
[normal]ansport is available for evening or Sunda
[normal]y activities;  these residents 
[normal]and visitors are 
[normal]isolated and 
